<L>__{interior aibileen's kitchen that night}
<A>__{minny, aibileen and skeeter sit at the kitchen table.}
<C>__{minny}
<D>__{aibileen and i done asked everbody we know. thirty one maids. everbody too scared, think we crazy...}
<C>__{skeeter}
<D>__{then we might as well stop!}
<C>__{minny}
<D>__{i got plenty a stories, miss skeeter. just write`em down and invent a maid that said it. we already making up everbody's name. make up the maids, too.}
<A>__{skeeter jumps up from her chair.}
<C>__{skeeter}
<D>__{we can't do that!}
<A>__{aibileen and minny lean back.}
<C>__{skeeter }
<D>__{i mean...i would never do that. it wouldn't be real. it's wrong.}
<C>__{aibileen}
<D>__{don't give up on us, miss skeeter.}
<A>__{skeeter softens and sits back down.}
<C>__{skeeter}
<D>__{i'm sorry. thank you both for trying.}
